<h1>Assignment 3 - CSS Color Conversions</h1>
<h2>1. Converting to RGB Format:</h2>

<h3>#61FA34 = rgb (97, 250, 52)</h3>
<p> 61 = 6 * 16^1 + 1 * 16^0 = 6 * 16 + 1 * 1 = 97</p>
<p> FA = F * 16^1 + A * 16^0 = 15 * 16 + 10 * 1 = 250</p>
<p> 34 = 3 * 16^1 + 4 * 16^0 = 3 * 16 + 4 * 1 = 52</p>

<h3>#34C6AB = rgb (52, 198, 171)</h3>
<p> 34 = 3 * 16^1 + 4 * 16^0 = 3 * 16 + 4 * 1 = 52</p>
<p> C6 = C * 16^1 + 6 * 16^0 = 12 * 16 + 6 * 1 = 198</p>
<p> AB = A * 16^1 + B * 16^0 = 10 * 16 + 11 * 1 = 171</p>

<h3>#B237FE = rgb (178, 55, 254)</h3>
<p> B2 = B * 16^1 + 2 * 16^0 = 11 * 16 + 2 * 1 = 178</p>
<p> 37 = 3 * 16^1 + 7 * 16^0 = 3 * 16 + 7 * 1 = 55</p>
<p> FE = F * 16^1 + E * 16^0 = 15 * 16 + 14 * 1 = 254</p>

<h3>#571AB4 = rgb (87, 26, 180)</h3>
<p> 57 = 5 * 16^1 + 7 * 16^0 = 5 * 16 + 7 * 1 = 87</p>
<p> 1A = 1 * 16^1 + A * 16^0 = 1 * 16 + 10 * 1 = 26</p>
<p> B4 = B * 16^1 + 4 * 16^0 = 12 * 16 + 4 * 1 = 180</p>

<h3>#FEB237 = rgb (254, 178, 55)</h3>
<p> FE = F * 16^1 + E * 16^0 = 15 * 16 + 14 * 1 = 87</p>
<p> B2 = B * 16^1 +2 * 16^0 = 11 * 16 + 2 * 1 = 178</p>
<p> 37 = 3 * 16^1 + 7 * 16^0 = 3 * 16 + 7 * 1 = 55</p>

<h3>#1AB457 = rgb (26, 180, 87)</h3>
<p> 1A = 1 * 16^1 + A * 16^0 = 1 * 16 + 10 * 1 = 26</p>
<p> B4 = B * 16^1 + 4 * 16^0 = 11 * 16 + 4 * 1 = 180</p>
<p> 57 = 5 * 16^1 + 7 * 16^0 = 5 * 16 + 7 * 1 = 87</p>

<h3>#AB4715 = rgb (171, 71, 21)</h3>
<p> AB = A * 16^1 + B * 16^0 = 10 * 16 + 11 * 1 = 171</p>
<p> 47 = 4 * 16^1 + 7 * 16^0 = 4 * 16 + 7 * 1 = 71</p>
<p> 15 = 0 * 16^1 + 15 * 16^0 = 0 * 16 + 15 * 1 = 15</p>


<h2>2. Converting to Hex Format:</h2>

<h3>rgb(213, 12, 112) = #D50C70</h3>
<p> 213 = 16 * <b>13</b> + <b>5</b> * 1 = D5 </p>
<p> 12 = 0 * <b>0</b> + <b>12</b> * 1 = 0C</p>
<p> 112 = 16 * <b>7</b> + 1 * <b>0</b> = 70</p>

<h3>rgb(22, 126, 52) = #167E34</h3>
<p> 22 = 16 * <b>1</b> + <b>6</b> * 1 = 16</p>
<p> 126 = 16 * <b>7</b> + <b>14</b> * 1 = 7E</p>
<p> 52 = 16 * <b>3</b> + <b>4</b> * 1 = 34</p>

<h3>rgb(213, 214, 41) = #D5D629</h3>
<p> 213 = 16 * <b>13</b> + <b>5</b> * 1 = D5</p>
<p> 214 = 16 * <b>13</b> + <b>6</b> * 1 = D6 </p>
<p> 41 =  16 * <b>2</b> + <b>9</b> * 1 = 29</p>

<h3>rgb(113, 22, 113) = #711671</h3>
<p> 113 = 16 * <b>7</b> + <b>1</b> * 1 = 71 </p>
<p> 22 = 16 * <b>1</b> + <b>6</b> * 1 = 16 </p>
<p> 113 = 16 * <b>7</b> + <b>1</b> * 1 = 71 </p>

<h3>rgb(126, 112, 172) = #7E70AC</h3>
<p> 126 = 16 * <b>7</b> + <b>14</b> * 1 = 7E </p>
<p> 112 = 16 * <b>7</b> + 1 * <b>0</b> = 70 </p>
<p> 172 = 16 * <b>10</b> + <b>12</b> * 1 = AC</p>

<h3>rgb(142, 24, 241) = #8E18F1</h3>
<p> 142 = 16 * <b>8</b> + <b>14</b> * 1 = 8E </p>
<p> 24 = 16 * <b>1</b> + <b>8</b> * 1 = 18 </p>
<p> 241 = 16 * <b>15</b> + 1 * <b>1</b> = F1 </p>

<h3>rgb(123, 32, 121) = #7B2079</h3>
<p> 123 = 16 * <b>7</b> + 1 * <b>11</b> = 7B</p>
<p> 32 = 16 * <b>2</b> + <b>0</b> * 0 = 20</p>
<p> 121 = 16 * <b>7</b> + <b>9</b> * 1 = 79</p>

<h3>rgb(127, 123, 224) = #7F7BE0</h3>
<p> 127 = 16 * <b>7</b> + <b>15</b> * 1 = 7F</p>
<p> 123 = 16 * <b>7</b> + 1 * <b>11</b> = 7B </p>
<p> 224 = 16 * <b>14</b> + 0 * <b>0</b> = E0 </p>

<h2>3. List 4 CSS properties that need color values:</h2>
<p> 4 properties that require color values are background color, opacity, outline color, and box shadow. </p>
